overview:
WoodDashEmpire.com features the biggest selection and best quality in dash kits and dashboard trim available on the internet.

All of out kits are OEM Approved and are made from a variety of materials including Real Wood, Real Carbon Fiber and Simulated Patterns. In addition to meeting OEM specifications, our experienced engineering staff take pride in developing each kit with design, fit and ease of installation in mind. Our factory match upgrade kits are produced with the best possible color & grain match to compliment the vehicles original interior wood trim. And to make ordering simple and convenient, we try to include several part options in a kit so that one part number can be used for various interior options such as digital / manual climate control.

So why settle for the interior the factory gave you? Whether you’re looking to revitalize an old dash, or add a classy custom look to your car, truck, or SUV, we believe that Wood Dash Empire has the answer.

Go ahead and see what the dealerships are charging for Wood Dash upgrades on their high end models and then come back to us. We’re sure you’ll buy from Wood Dash Empire…because chances are those dealerships are too!
